I did this recipe with the following tweeks which I recommend. Follow the recipe through the "saute shrimp" step. At that point remove the shrimp to prevent over cooking. Deglaze the pan with a small amount of white wine, reduce until slightly thickened and then incorporate the additional butter. It won't take as much butter as the recipe calls for to achieve sauce consistency.

